        "timestamp": "2018-07-20 15:05:43.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nHow do you guys think we should handle duplicated counterparts of the drools repo, removing these parts from policy-endpoints, policy-core and policy-utils projects?\n\nReason for asking is that I have aaf/security in policy-endpoints module in drools repo for this sprint.",
