        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-07-20 16:06:50.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nJust as a note, I think when we remove from drools-pdp, we will have to remove cross-repo, I think there are usages in policy-engine, and drools-applications.",
