        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2018-07-20 16:37:32.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nYes, the intention is to remove the from drools repo and replace all references to the drools repo classes (in drools-pdp, drools-applications...etc) with references to these new classes in common",
